   -n nops          specifies the no. of operations per process (default 1)
   -p nproc         specifies the no. of processes (default 1)
   -r               specifies random name padding
   -s seed          specifies the seed for the random generator (default random)
   -v               specifies verbose mode
   -w               zeros frequencies of non-write operations
   -z               zeros frequencies of all operations
   -S               prints the table of operations (omitting zero frequency)
   -H               prints usage and exits
